create a school management app database schema. there will be admin, teachers. each teacher can have multiple subjects, lessons and classes. and in each class, there will be students. a student has a parent, grade, class, exam or assignment, results and attendance. Parents can have multiple children. each grade have multiple students and classes. each class has a grade, supervisor(teacher), multiple students and lessons. a lesson has a class, subject, teacher, multiple exams and assignments. and each exam and assignment has a result. in the attendance table, the student will be present or absent for the given lesson